#: mobile.lang:22
msgid "Firefox Home for <span>iPhone</span>"
msgstr "Firefox Home ar gyfer <span>iPhone</span>"

#: mobile.lang:25
msgid "Access your Firefox history, bookmarks and open tabs on your iPhone."
msgstr ""
"Cael mynediad i'ch hanes, nodau tudalen a tabiau agored ar Firefox ar eich "
"iPhone."

#: mobile.lang:28
