msgstr "Llwytho i Lawr Beta ar gyfer Android"

#: mobile.lang:41
msgid "Download"
msgstr "Llwytho i Lawr"

#: mobile.lang:44
msgid "for"
msgstr "ar gyfer"

#: mobile.lang:47
msgid "Free from iTunes"
msgstr "Am Ddim o iTunes"

#: mobile.lang:50
msgid ""
"You’ll get to experience cutting-edge features and provide feedback to help "
"refine and polish what will be in the final release."
msgstr ""
"Byddwch yn cael profi nodweddion diweddaraf a darparu adborth i helpu i "
"wella'r fersiwn terfynol."

#: mobile.lang:53
msgid "Developer Tools"
msgstr "Offer Datblygwyr"

#: mobile.lang:56
msgid ""
"You can install the mobile version of Firefox to our desktop computer in "
"order to test, provide feedback, and build add-ons."
msgstr ""
"Mae modd gosod y fersiwn symudol o Firefox ar ein cyfrifiadur bwrdd gwaith "
"er mwyn profi, darparu adborth ac adeiladu ychwanegion."

#: mobile.lang:59
msgid "Connect With Firefox for Mobile:"
msgstr "Cysylltwch gyda Firefox for Mobile:"

#: mobile.lang:62
msgid "Monthly newsletter"
msgstr "Cylchlythyr misol"

#: mobile.lang:65
msgid "Follow us"
msgstr "Dilynwch ni"

#: mobile.lang:68
msgid "Become a fan"
msgstr "Dod yn gefnogwr"

#: mobile.lang:72
msgid ""
"Firefox is full of innovations that let you type less, browse more and get "
"to the Web quickly and easily."
msgstr ""
"Mae Firefox yn llawn arloesedd, sy'n gadael i chi deipio llai, pori mwy a "
"chael at y We'n haws ac yn gynt."

#: mobile.lang:76
msgid "Freedom from typing"
msgstr "Rhyddid rhag teipio"

#: mobile.lang:80
msgid ""
"The Awesome Screen learns your favorite sites so you can browse with little "
"or no typing."
msgstr ""
"Mae'r Sgrin Rhagorol yn dysgu'ch hoff wefannau fel bo modd i chi bori gyda "
"llai o deipio."

#: mobile.lang:84
msgid "Best of both worlds"
msgstr "Y gorau o ddau fyd"

#: mobile.lang:87
msgid ""
"Firefox for Android is now redesigned and optimized for the way you browse "
"on phones and tablets."
msgstr ""
"Mae Firefox ar gyfer Android wedi ei ail lunio a'i wella ar gyfer y ffordd "
"rydych yn pori ar ffonau a thabledi."

#: mobile.lang:90
msgid "Browse quick and easy"
msgstr "Pori sydyn a hawdd"

#: mobile.lang:93
msgid ""
"Features like Sync, tabbed browsing and one-touch bookmarking mean "
"everything you want is close at hand."
msgstr ""
"Mae nodweddion fel Sync, pori tabiau a nod tudalen un cyffyrddiad yn golygu "
"fod popeth wrth law."

#: mobile.lang:96
msgid "<a %s>Need help?</a> Visit our Firefox for Android Support site."
msgstr ""
"<a %s>Angen help?</a> Ewch i'n gwefan cymorth Firefox ar gyfer Android."

#: mobile.lang:99
msgid "Download and test the build that’s right for you."
msgstr "Llwythwch i lawr a phrofi'r fersiwn sydd orau ar eich cyfer."

#: mobile.lang:102
msgid "See all our channels for mobile »"
msgstr "Gwelwch ein holl sianeli symudo »"

